+              Students were abandoning the study abroad portal and going to
+              advisors directly. I led two-phase research with 14 participants
+              (faculty + students) and found: information overload made users
+              feel "lost," financial details were nearly unfindable, and 4 of 10
+              students cited outdated design as a reason for distrust. Redesigned
+              the IA, collapsed a confusing 3-tab system into one unified search,
+              and delivered a high-fidelity prototype.
